summary: Realistic Teeth fix for Inconsequential NPCs
descriptionHtml:
This file is to make life a bit easier for those using both Inconsequential NPCs and Realistic Teeth. There's no new assets, only those modified by realistic teeth patcher.

I have extracted Facegeom data from Inconsequential NPCs with BSA Extractor, ran them through Realistic Teeth Face Converter Tool, and packed the resulting file as 7z. I haven't noticed any issues, feel free to bring up anything I may have missed so I can correct it if necessary.
author: None
